Plot: A rising country-music songwriter works with a fallen star to work their way to fame, causing romantic complications along the way.
Title: Country Strong
Actors: Gwyneth Paltrow, Tim McGraw, Garrett Hedlund, Leighton Meester
tomatoConsensus: The cast gives it their all, and Paltrow handles her songs with aplomb, but Country Strong's cliched, disjointed screenplay hits too many bum notes.
Awards: Nominated for 1 Oscar. Another 1 win & 6 nominations.
